>>SOURCE FORMAT IS FREE
IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. FREE-FORMAT-TEST.
* Free format COBOL for testing

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-COUNTER PIC 9(4) VALUE 0.
01 WS-MESSAGE PIC X(50) VALUE 'FREE FORMAT TEST'.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN-PARA.
    DISPLAY WS-MESSAGE
    ADD 1 TO WS-COUNTER
    DISPLAY 'Counter: ' WS-COUNTER
    STOP RUN.
